WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.179
Hail Jesus and Mary, dear followers of the "Croatia for Life" YouTube channel.

00:00:16.179 --> 00:00:20.147
We are here in the parish of St. Josip in Trešnjevka

00:00:20.147 --> 00:00:24.701
as part of our 6th conference for life „Now choose life!“

00:00:24.701 --> 00:00:27.461
Our guest today is Patricia Sandoval.

00:00:27.461 --> 00:00:32.252
She is a worldknown pro-life and purity speaker.

00:00:32.252 --> 00:00:33.966
Patricia welcome!

00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:38.342
Thank you so much for having me on the show and greetings to everybody watching.

00:00:38.342 --> 00:00:43.037
It was a real pleasure to spend some time with you these days

00:00:43.037 --> 00:00:47.156
and to hear something about your life

00:00:47.156 --> 00:00:51.035
and I would really love if you can share some of that

00:00:51.035 --> 00:00:54.353
to our listeners and watchers.

00:00:54.353 --> 00:00:59.347
So I travel the world telling my story in reparation

00:00:59.347 --> 00:01:04.483
for the damage I've caused in the pro-abortion industry.

00:01:04.483 --> 00:01:10.150
So when I was a little girl the pro-abortion industry came to my school.

00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:12.828
My family and I did not practice our faith.

00:01:12.828 --> 00:01:16.067
I had no formation at home on sexuality.

00:01:16.067 --> 00:01:20.302
I didn't know that my virginity and my purity was something that I had to protect

00:01:20.302 --> 00:01:22.268
and take care of that, it was a treasure.

00:01:22.268 --> 00:01:25.115
My parents couldn't give me that formation because they themselves

00:01:25.115 --> 00:01:26.921
didn't receive it when they were little.

00:01:26.921 --> 00:01:34.253
So the abortion industry basically gave me a disordered sexual education course

00:01:34.253 --> 00:01:37.638
called responsible sex, which doesn't exist

00:01:37.638 --> 00:01:41.292
and they spoke about abortion being a woman's right,

00:01:41.292 --> 00:01:46.546
they spoke about „it's a woman's body, it's her choice“

00:01:46.546 --> 00:01:50.902
and they gave us a lot of condoms and birth control pill

00:01:50.902 --> 00:01:57.713
to make us curious about sex and they encouraged us to start experimenting sexually.

00:01:57.713 --> 00:01:59.674
But it's all a trap.

00:01:59.674 --> 00:02:03.346
Because they need a certain amount of abortions every month

00:02:03.346 --> 00:02:07.709
and what they do is they go into the schools, they go after the little ones.

00:02:07.709 --> 00:02:13.142
They say: „Since parents aren't educating children on sexuality at home,

00:02:13.142 --> 00:02:15.198
we will be their sexual educators.“

00:02:15.198 --> 00:02:20.000
What happened to me when I was a teenager is, I met my first boyfriend,

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.654
I was not a virgin and I was pregnant three times.

00:02:24.654 --> 00:02:29.297
The three times I decided to have an abortion.

00:02:29.297 --> 00:02:32.583
So I had three abortions in a year and a half.

00:02:32.583 --> 00:02:36.385
Number one I thought that a baby destroyed your dreams.

00:02:36.385 --> 00:02:41.950
I, you know, I was a straight A student, I wanted to travel the world, I wanted to be successful.

00:02:41.950 --> 00:02:46.355
The first time I was pregnant I thought my life was completely over.

00:02:46.355 --> 00:02:51.041
I believed that a stay-at-home mom, a mom that just cooked and cleaned all day,

00:02:51.041 --> 00:02:53.404
that's what I thought, was a domestic slave.

00:02:53.404 --> 00:02:57.425
My parents divorced when I was little and my mom left

00:02:57.425 --> 00:03:00.092
because she said that she was just serving everybody

00:03:00.092 --> 00:03:02.340
and she was throwing her life away.

00:03:02.340 --> 00:03:05.285
She wanted to live her life.

00:03:05.285 --> 00:03:09.213
So I believe the same thing when I was pregnant, that my life was over.

00:03:09.213 --> 00:03:14.511
And when I went to go have abortions they lied to me at the abortion clinic.

00:03:14.511 --> 00:03:16.787
They told me that it was just a sack of tissue,

00:03:16.787 --> 00:03:20.518
it's a clump of cells and they never told me about post-abortion syndrome.

00:03:20.518 --> 00:03:28.114
After each abortion I suffered depression, anxiety, sadness, suicidal thoughts.

00:03:28.114 --> 00:03:30.751
I mean there was times I really wanted to take my life.

00:03:30.751 --> 00:03:36.172
Eating disorders, my emotions were like a roller coaster.

00:03:36.172 --> 00:03:39.952
I'd be angry all the time, all of a sudden I'd cry all the time.

00:03:39.952 --> 00:03:43.903
And my boyfriend also was going through post-abortion syndrome.

00:03:43.903 --> 00:03:47.872
He was experimenting nightmares, anxiety, deep sadness.

00:03:47.872 --> 00:03:50.027
He felt like there was something missing.

00:03:50.027 --> 00:03:54.752
At one point he even started drinking alcohol and he started to try drugs, cocaine.

00:03:54.752 --> 00:03:58.426
That are also symptoms of post-abortion syndrome:

00:03:58.426 --> 00:04:03.344
drugs, alcohol, gambling even, suicidal thoughts.

00:04:03.344 --> 00:04:07.874
80% of women after an abortion they want to take their life.

00:04:07.874 --> 00:04:12.235
And I was experimenting these things but I didn't connect it to my abortions.

00:04:12.235 --> 00:04:15.952
Then I went to work for the abortion industry,

00:04:15.952 --> 00:04:18.754
still thinking that abortion was a woman's choice,

00:04:18.754 --> 00:04:24.176
it's a woman's right but it was there where I saw the truth about abortion.

00:04:24.176 --> 00:04:28.878
It was in the abortion industry where I thought I was helping women

00:04:28.878 --> 00:04:32.553
and I didn't think they were babies until you were 5 months pregnant

00:04:32.553 --> 00:04:34.229
because I learned that in school.

00:04:34.229 --> 00:04:36.885
They trained me how to hide my words.

00:04:36.885 --> 00:04:41.536
I had to never say baby, father, mother, he, she.

00:04:41.536 --> 00:04:44.880
I couldn't use the word fetus because that gave human dignity

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:48.386
and I couldn't help women if they were crying.

00:04:48.386 --> 00:04:50.377
I had to ignore their tears.

00:04:50.377 --> 00:04:55.813
It was when I had to assist the abortionist for the first time that I saw truth.

00:04:55.813 --> 00:05:02.382
We did 50 abortions a week but the first abortion I assisted

00:05:02.382 --> 00:05:06.529
was a young girl that was 15 years old and she was three months pregnant.

00:05:06.529 --> 00:05:13.948
I stood behind the abortionist and he took out very, very sharp instruments

00:05:13.948 --> 00:05:16.739
and she was kicking and screaming and crying.

00:05:17.807 --> 00:05:20.421
And during the abortion it looked very unsafe

00:05:20.421 --> 00:05:23.193
because she was kicking and I thought:

00:05:23.193 --> 00:05:26.957
„Oh he's going to take the sharp instrument out the vacuum machine“.

00:05:26.957 --> 00:05:32.036
And I just saw the abortionist duck in and I thought:

00:05:32.036 --> 00:05:34.955
„Wait a minute why isn't he stopping.

00:05:34.955 --> 00:05:38.278
Wait a minute he can't see inside of the womb and what he's doing,

00:05:38.278 --> 00:05:41.634
he can't see if he took out the whole clump of cells,

00:05:41.634 --> 00:05:44.238
he can't see if he's perforating her womb.“

00:05:44.238 --> 00:05:50.649
And then I realized how unsafe abortion is because it's a complete blind man surgery

00:05:50.649 --> 00:05:56.740
and that's why millions of women have died after an abortion throughout many years.

00:05:56.740 --> 00:06:00.264
That's why women can't have children, they're infertile.

00:06:00.264 --> 00:06:04.024
There are women that have their womb perforated after an abortion.

00:06:04.024 --> 00:06:08.867
There are women that even have their intestines perforated after an abortion.

00:06:08.867 --> 00:06:10.687
I've heard many testimonies like that.

00:06:10.687 --> 00:06:16.705
And since he couldn't see what he was doing, I had to be his eyes.

00:06:16.705 --> 00:06:19.771
And I was taken into a little room in the back of the clinic

00:06:19.771 --> 00:06:25.493
and I literally had to look for the body parts of the baby, which was very shocking to me.

00:06:25.493 --> 00:06:29.373
And I saw little hands, I saw legs and little feet

00:06:29.373 --> 00:06:35.572
and when the head was held up to the light I saw that the baby had little eyes, nose, ears.

00:06:35.572 --> 00:06:40.545
And the baby's mouth was wide open because this baby was screaming to defend its life

00:06:40.545 --> 00:06:43.613
but the baby was completely voiceless.

00:06:43.613 --> 00:06:49.622
And she threw that baby away in the garbage and the five parts were found.

00:06:49.622 --> 00:06:51.854
We had a five parts.

00:06:51.854 --> 00:06:55.972
Working behind the doors was a complete Holocaust of killing of children.

00:06:55.972 --> 00:06:59.096
Women would bleed to death, faint.

00:06:59.096 --> 00:07:05.116
And I was just looking for body parts all day and I realized that they lied to me.

00:07:05.116 --> 00:07:08.234
That I didn't abort three sack of tissues.

00:07:08.234 --> 00:07:10.086
I aborted my three children.

00:07:10.086 --> 00:07:13.918
And that they lied to women, they lied to men and they destroy families

00:07:13.918 --> 00:07:16.844
and it was very, very devastating.

00:07:16.844 --> 00:07:19.903
I didn't remember God.

00:07:19.903 --> 00:07:23.668
I mean, I knew who God was when I was little because I was baptized Catholic.

00:07:23.668 --> 00:07:30.594
So I started to use drugs to numb the pain and I was so addicted to cocaine and crack.

00:07:30.594 --> 00:07:35.995
I lost everything and I lived three years with the Mexican cartel on the streets.

00:07:35.995 --> 00:07:39.623
And one day I thought I was going to die.

00:07:39.623 --> 00:07:45.870
I had nothing to eat and I was crying because I thought my life was going to be over.

00:07:45.870 --> 00:07:49.267
That was the first time in my life that I felt the presence of God the Father

00:07:49.267 --> 00:07:52.347
who looked down on me with pity.

00:07:52.347 --> 00:07:57.425
I felt His presence very strongly and I cried out to God and I asked him to forgive me.

00:07:57.425 --> 00:08:02.224
Very quickly a woman, a waitress came out of her job,

00:08:02.224 --> 00:08:07.078
her restaurant and she looked at me with so much love and mercy.

00:08:07.078 --> 00:08:11.194
She said: „Jesus loves you, I was praying for you in the restaurant

00:08:11.194 --> 00:08:14.443
and I saw you crying on the street.

00:08:14.443 --> 00:08:18.752
God told me that He will never abandon you and that He will always be with you

00:08:18.752 --> 00:08:20.967
and He forgives everything you do.“

00:08:20.967 --> 00:08:25.513
Thanks to her I came back home but it was really my mother's prayers.

00:08:25.513 --> 00:08:30.212
My mother prayed for me three years on her knees before the Blessed Sacrament,

00:08:30.212 --> 00:08:32.166
fasting and praying.

00:08:32.166 --> 00:08:35.445
It was God's Divine Mercy in my mother's prayers that I

00:08:35.445 --> 00:08:40.613
was rescued and that I'm here today. 
We are so happy to have you here.

00:08:40.613 --> 00:08:48.769
I've noticed that you also had some kind of disorder with your hair.

00:08:48.769 --> 00:08:54.009
Can you please explain this and how many kilos did you have

00:08:54.009 --> 00:08:57.048
and everything because of the post-abortive syndrome?

00:08:57.048 --> 00:09:01.136
Right. When I was little, when my mom left I was 12.

00:09:01.136 --> 00:09:04.809
The divorce of my parents, and I still suffer from that as an adult,

00:09:04.809 --> 00:09:11.730
so the divorce of my parents really wounded me so I started to pull out my hair as a child.

00:09:11.730 --> 00:09:15.848
And once the post-abortion syndrome started to happen,

00:09:15.848 --> 00:09:21.706
it got worse to the point when I was on drugs on the street I completely was bald at the end.

00:09:21.706 --> 00:09:26.156
Like when I hit my lowest point, because I was always on drugs.

00:09:26.156 --> 00:09:28.102
I was bones.

00:09:28.102 --> 00:09:33.507
I was literally like a skeleton walking through the Earth, lost, dead, with no life.

00:09:33.507 --> 00:09:35.585
I was a dead woman walking.

00:09:35.585 --> 00:09:38.892
Now you can see that Jesus has given me full life.

00:09:38.892 --> 00:09:40.837
I mean I just feel like I'm full of life.

00:09:40.837 --> 00:09:46.819
And so you know I think couples that are together

00:09:46.819 --> 00:09:52.293
and that are having issues or marriages that are having difficulties

00:09:52.293 --> 00:09:56.093
have no idea how much divorce affects a child.

00:09:56.093 --> 00:09:57.940
It really wounds you.

00:09:57.940 --> 00:10:01.266
I could say, I mean I know abortion is terrible and it's horrible,

00:10:01.266 --> 00:10:03.441
I didn't know what I was doing when I had abortions

00:10:03.441 --> 00:10:08.475
but I could tell you that the greatest wound in my heart till today is the divorce of my parents.

00:10:08.475 --> 00:10:10.867
It's very hard.

00:10:10.867 --> 00:10:18.079
I remember that you said that you were pregnant 4 months for your first abortion,

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:22.628
that your boyfriend was very happy about that.

00:10:22.628 --> 00:10:31.436
So he wasn't put in this group of people who are not supportive to partners,

00:10:31.436 --> 00:10:33.963
who don't want a child and everything.

00:10:33.963 --> 00:10:35.966
He was the opposite of it.

00:10:35.966 --> 00:10:37.682
Can you tell us more about that?

00:10:37.682 --> 00:10:44.127
Yes. I told my boyfriend about the first pregnancy and he was very happy to be a father.

00:10:44.127 --> 00:10:49.996
All the fear that I had, oh my life is over, you know, I'm not successful.

00:10:49.996 --> 00:10:53.193
When he told me 'you're not alone', 'I'm going to take care of you',

00:10:53.193 --> 00:10:56.455
'you don't worry, I'm going to be responsible'.

00:10:56.455 --> 00:11:01.794
That gave me so much comfort and encouragement to continue my pregnancy.

00:11:01.794 --> 00:11:05.891
And I feel like most women have abortions because

00:11:05.891 --> 00:11:09.330
they feel alone or they're abandoned or they're forced to have an abortion

00:11:09.330 --> 00:11:12.169
or their male partner is very passive.

00:11:12.169 --> 00:11:17.650
Men today want to support women so much and I feel that it's gone over the limit.

00:11:17.650 --> 00:11:21.096
Like you know men are 'I'll support what you want to do'

00:11:21.096 --> 00:11:24.386
and sometimes they're not good things like abortion.

00:11:24.386 --> 00:11:27.259
So there are men that are indifferent or passive.

00:11:27.259 --> 00:11:31.183
And working with women and men who have had abortions,

00:11:31.183 --> 00:11:35.743
I could tell you that 90% of abortions are probably because the man is in crisis

00:11:35.743 --> 00:11:41.122
and he's scared to be a father and he doesn't want that pregnancy to continue.

00:11:41.122 --> 00:11:43.260
He wants that abortion.

00:11:43.260 --> 00:11:50.871
I feel that abortion is also a male issue obviously and men also need to go heal.

00:11:50.871 --> 00:11:56.967
But when he comforted me, my boyfriend, that gave me the power to continue my pregnancy

00:11:56.967 --> 00:12:00.718
until my friends came over one day and then the fear came back.

00:12:00.718 --> 00:12:03.800
They told me I was making the worst mistake of my life, what are you doing…

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:06.940
And then I decided to have an abortion without telling him the truth.

00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:11.835
So Patricia you said about your boyfriend that he was supportive,

00:12:11.835 --> 00:12:20.040
he wanted to take care of you and you choose to have an abortion

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:26.487
because someone told you that it is your right and that you should do it

00:12:26.487 --> 00:12:29.504
and it's your choice your body.

00:12:29.504 --> 00:12:33.761
Those were also arguments for doing abortion.

00:12:33.761 --> 00:12:36.995
Right and I think the root of all abortion is fear.

00:12:36.995 --> 00:12:41.193
A lot of women think 'my parents are going to get very angry,

00:12:41.193 --> 00:12:45.157
they're going to kick me out of the house, I don't have a job

00:12:45.157 --> 00:12:51.613
or I can't financially support this child or I'm alone or even for shame'.

00:12:51.613 --> 00:12:55.216
You know there's shame because what are people going to think about me,

00:12:55.216 --> 00:12:57.689
I'm not in a stable relationship…

00:12:57.689 --> 00:13:00.287
I feel like the root of it all is fear.

00:13:00.287 --> 00:13:04.018
If women only knew that there's a lot of help,

00:13:04.018 --> 00:13:07.872
there's a lot of pregnancy centers in different parts of the world and cities…

00:13:07.872 --> 00:13:10.306
We just don't know where they are.

00:13:10.306 --> 00:13:12.287
We need to know where they are.

00:13:12.287 --> 00:13:19.614
And these centers offer spiritual help, emotional help, financial help for mother and baby.

00:13:19.614 --> 00:13:28.342
So I think these women don't know all the help and support that they have, that there is help.

00:13:28.342 --> 00:13:32.230
I tell women that are pregnant and they're thinking about having an abortion,

00:13:32.230 --> 00:13:36.812
I say 'yes, your parents might get mad at you, they might be angry,

00:13:36.812 --> 00:13:40.568
and yes people will judge you and point you.'

00:13:40.568 --> 00:13:43.468
But once you have that baby it will all change.

00:13:43.468 --> 00:13:48.315
That baby will be the light and the joy of your family and your parents will forget.

00:13:48.315 --> 00:13:51.665
Your parents will be the best grandparents and they'll forget.

00:13:51.665 --> 00:13:54.980
And that's what usually happens during the pregnancy of the young girl that's in crisis.

00:13:54.980 --> 00:13:59.718
Her family members are mad but when that baby is born it's the light of the family.

00:13:59.718 --> 00:14:04.203
I also think that maybe they're not mad, they're also in fear...

00:14:04.203 --> 00:14:07.074
Or disappointed. They're disappointed.

00:14:07.074 --> 00:14:09.362
Because that's not what we want for our children

00:14:09.362 --> 00:14:11.562
but unfortunately it can happen to anybody.

00:14:11.562 --> 00:14:16.537
I always tell parents, we want the best for our child

00:14:16.537 --> 00:14:24.109
but you need to tell your child 'I don't want for you to get pregnant at an early age'.

00:14:24.109 --> 00:14:31.777
You need to teach them about chastity but if this were to happen, I will support life.

00:14:31.777 --> 00:14:36.375
I had a friend of mine, she's a single mother, she has a daughter

00:14:36.375 --> 00:14:41.217
and she said the reason I did not have an abortion is because when I was a child

00:14:41.217 --> 00:14:45.454
my father said I want you to be pure until marriage, I want you to live a chastity life.

00:14:45.454 --> 00:14:50.437
But if you were to get pregnant, never have an abortion,

00:14:50.437 --> 00:14:54.864
always come to me and I will always support you, no matter what.

00:14:54.864 --> 00:14:57.236
Even though I'm disappointed, I will support you.

00:14:57.236 --> 00:15:00.706
And she remembered those words of her father 20 years later

00:15:00.706 --> 00:15:05.553
and that's why her child is alive today because her father said that.

00:15:05.553 --> 00:15:08.864
We are disappointed, we're angry

00:15:08.864 --> 00:15:14.335
but we have to remember that life is a gift no matter what the circumstances are.

00:15:14.335 --> 00:15:17.975
And that we need to support these women.

00:15:17.975 --> 00:15:23.182
So you came back home and your mother told you that she was praying

00:15:23.182 --> 00:15:28.782
in front of the Blessed Sacrament for your life and for you to come home.

00:15:28.782 --> 00:15:31.810
And what then?

00:15:31.810 --> 00:15:36.342
My mother took me to a confession, thank God and I went to daily mass.

00:15:36.342 --> 00:15:40.470
God healed me through the power of the sacraments.

00:15:40.470 --> 00:15:45.495
He healed the wanting to kill myself, the drug addiction, the depression,

00:15:45.495 --> 00:15:47.949
anxiety all that, even the hair pulling.

00:15:47.949 --> 00:15:53.107
I mean, I still do it sometimes but it's been much much much healed.

00:15:53.107 --> 00:15:55.147
But I couldn't forgive my abortions.

00:15:55.147 --> 00:15:58.838
That was very hard because not only did I know that I killed but I saw it.

00:15:58.838 --> 00:16:01.264
I saw what goes behind the doors of an abortion clinic.

00:16:01.264 --> 00:16:04.468
It's hell on Earth literally.

00:16:04.468 --> 00:16:06.749
And I couldn't forgive myself.

00:16:06.749 --> 00:16:10.511
I knew the priest forgave me because I would confess it over and over.

00:16:10.511 --> 00:16:14.252
I could hear that God forgave me but there was something missing.

00:16:14.252 --> 00:16:18.408
And when I went to this healing retreat and it's for men and women,

00:16:18.408 --> 00:16:23.772
usually all post-abortion healing retreats are for men and women because men need to heal too.

00:16:23.772 --> 00:16:29.049
I actually during a prayer saw my three aborted children.

00:16:29.049 --> 00:16:33.998
I saw my daughter Mariana, my son Emmanuel and my little girl Rosario.

00:16:33.998 --> 00:16:41.304
And they said: „Mama, we are alive in God's glory and we're praying for you.“

00:16:41.304 --> 00:16:47.779
And then, just when I woke up from that vision to feel from murder to Mama,

00:16:47.779 --> 00:16:51.500
I thought that God's mercy was so great and that my children forgave me.

00:16:51.500 --> 00:16:57.983
That gave me the confidence to forgive myself and I healed so much.

00:16:57.983 --> 00:17:01.903
If it wasn't for that healing retreat I wouldn't be doing what I'm doing today.

00:17:01.903 --> 00:17:06.836
That retreat changed my life and that Retreat gave me my purpose.

00:17:06.836 --> 00:17:09.873
You know sometimes we don't know what our purpose in life is,

00:17:09.873 --> 00:17:12.248
we don't know what God's will is.

00:17:12.248 --> 00:17:17.508
But out of my misery, God used my misery to give my life salvation,

00:17:17.508 --> 00:17:19.257
my life purpose.

00:17:19.257 --> 00:17:22.487
So I'm really grateful for that healing retreat.

00:17:22.487 --> 00:17:28.215
I'm also doing a healing retreat for the women who have had an abortion

00:17:28.215 --> 00:17:36.724
and it's really fruitful and it's really blessed when they gave names to their children.

00:17:36.724 --> 00:17:43.414
So can you please explain to us the symbolism of the three names?

00:17:43.414 --> 00:17:49.921
Right. So the scripture says, God says 'I called you by your name before you were even born'.

00:17:49.921 --> 00:17:52.008
So God gave us an identity.

00:17:52.008 --> 00:17:57.091
He gave us a name and women have to remember that those souls,

00:17:57.091 --> 00:17:59.024
those souls are their children.

00:17:59.024 --> 00:18:01.966
They're children and they have an identity.

00:18:01.966 --> 00:18:08.569
By praying to God, I recommend women to pray before the Blessed Sacrament or during mass

00:18:08.569 --> 00:18:13.702
and ask God what is the sex of my child, was it a girl or a boy.

00:18:13.702 --> 00:18:16.726
And God will let the woman know.

00:18:16.726 --> 00:18:24.200
God will let the woman know and then name your children, give them the identity.

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:28.712
How did you choose your names?

00:18:28.712 --> 00:18:34.184
Mariana I chose because it's the name of the Blessed Virgin Mary

00:18:34.184 --> 00:18:36.752
and her mother St. Anne – Mariana.

00:18:36.752 --> 00:18:42.348
Emmanuel means God with us, and Rosario is in honor of the Rosary,

00:18:42.348 --> 00:18:45.322
the Holy Rosary that is a powerful weapon.

00:18:45.322 --> 00:18:47.150
So about the rosary.

00:18:47.150 --> 00:18:54.946
You pray the rosary, you think it's a source of wisdom and source of peace?

00:18:54.946 --> 00:18:58.971
Yes, the rosary is non-negotiable for me and my family.

00:18:58.971 --> 00:19:01.988
We actually pray it as a family because it has more power.

00:19:01.988 --> 00:19:07.484
There are priests and bishop that said that the evil one cannot attack the little children

00:19:07.484 --> 00:19:12.211
as much when the family prays the Holy Rosary at home together.

00:19:12.211 --> 00:19:18.278
And actually there's a book called the Secret of the Rosary by the St. Louis de Monfort

00:19:18.278 --> 00:19:25.474
and in this book our Lady reveals to St. Louis de Monfort that if you pray your Rosary by yourself,

00:19:25.474 --> 00:19:27.838
you gain the merit of one Rosary.

00:19:27.838 --> 00:19:36.213
But if you pray the rosary with a community or with your family, say we're family of four,

00:19:36.213 --> 00:19:38.758
and I gained the merit of four rosaries.

00:19:38.758 --> 00:19:42.531
So it's much powerful if you pray the rosary with a 100 people in your church.

00:19:42.531 --> 00:19:45.250
It's like you gave our lady a 100 rosaries.

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:47.809
So it's a powerful weapon against evil.

00:19:47.809 --> 00:19:52.720
There's promises that our Lady gives to those who are devoted to the rosary.

00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:57.132
And it's also a way to talk to your Mama every day.

00:19:57.132 --> 00:20:02.131
Most of us are married and we don't live with our mothers and we call them on the phone.

00:20:02.131 --> 00:20:06.124
So the rosary it's like calling your Mama to heaven.

00:20:06.124 --> 00:20:10.779
And when you hold the Rosary in your hand and you have your Rosary in your pocket,

00:20:10.779 --> 00:20:13.572
it's like our Lady's holding your hand all day.

00:20:13.572 --> 00:20:18.531
So it's just after the Holy Mass, I think it's the most powerful prayer.

00:20:18.531 --> 00:20:21.288
That's so good. Thank you so much, I really love this.

00:20:21.288 --> 00:20:27.411
So can you please tell us how old were you when you gone to the healing retreat

00:20:27.411 --> 00:20:33.932
and after that how long passed when you felt ready to go outside?

00:20:33.932 --> 00:20:40.409
And how it all started for you to have this public speaking?

00:20:40.409 --> 00:20:47.778
After my mother started to pray for me and I was rescued out the street I was 22 years old

00:20:47.778 --> 00:20:52.756
and I did my healing retreat at 27.

00:20:52.756 --> 00:20:57.053
But I was healing all of the abortion, going to healing, masses, retreats…

00:20:57.053 --> 00:21:02.939
I mean I was going to daily Mass so I felt like a lot of healing was going on in my life.

00:21:02.939 --> 00:21:07.297
But then, when I was 26 years old is when I went to my healing retreat

00:21:07.297 --> 00:21:12.267
and that completely healed me from abortion.

00:21:12.267 --> 00:21:14.747
It was amazing.

00:21:14.747 --> 00:21:20.865
I didn't know that I was still angry at many people or at myself.

00:21:20.865 --> 00:21:25.297
I had to learn to forgive my abortionist that lied to me.

00:21:25.297 --> 00:21:30.219
I had to forgive all the sexual educators and the abortionist that came to my school.

00:21:30.219 --> 00:21:34.376
I had to forgive the workers that lied to me,

00:21:34.376 --> 00:21:40.069
even the people that I worked with in Planned Parenthood - the manager that lied.

00:21:40.069 --> 00:21:44.572
I had to forgive people thar were involved with my abortion because it's murder.

00:21:44.572 --> 00:21:51.813
And it's really, really important that men and women go to a healing retreat

00:21:51.813 --> 00:21:54.866
because it took me 5 years to go.

00:21:54.866 --> 00:21:58.296
My mother would say you need to go to an abortion healing retreat and I would say:

00:21:58.296 --> 00:22:03.859
„No mama, I already went to confession, I went to all these healing masses, I go to daily mass,

00:22:03.859 --> 00:22:05.571
I don't need that, that's not for me.“

00:22:05.571 --> 00:22:07.484
But there was still shame.

00:22:07.484 --> 00:22:10.962
The reason I didn't go is because I still felt so much shame.

00:22:10.962 --> 00:22:16.161
Even when I got arrived at my healing retreat, I arrived on a Friday.

00:22:16.161 --> 00:22:20.616
I was in the parking lot and I put reverse on my car and I was going to leave

00:22:20.616 --> 00:22:24.206
and I said this is not for me, I don't need this.

00:22:24.206 --> 00:22:28.086
And a priest stopped me in the parking lot and opened my car door

00:22:28.086 --> 00:22:31.206
and opened my trunk and took my luggage out and he said: „Welcome.“

00:22:31.206 --> 00:22:34.316
And I was stuck.

00:22:34.316 --> 00:22:40.838
But it's so important because abortion damages the five senses of the women.

00:22:40.838 --> 00:22:45.835
So when she goes into an abortion clinic, she sees everything around her.

00:22:45.835 --> 00:22:51.080
She hears the vacuum sound, so the sight and the hearing.

00:22:51.080 --> 00:22:52.848
She touches the abortionist, his hand.

00:22:52.848 --> 00:22:54.849
She touches abortionist.

00:22:54.849 --> 00:22:57.730
She hears abortion, she sees abortion, she smells abortion because abortion has a smell.

00:22:57.730 --> 00:23:00.827
It smells like death in that clinic.

00:23:00.827 --> 00:23:06.134
So when a woman goes to confession she's receiving God's mercy through one sense

00:23:06.134 --> 00:23:08.651
but all the other is damaged.

00:23:08.651 --> 00:23:12.067
Her memory, her emotion is damaged.

00:23:12.067 --> 00:23:16.129
So just a five minute confession, it's not enough.

00:23:16.129 --> 00:23:23.228
These abortion healing retreats help heal the whole woman and the whole man.

00:23:23.228 --> 00:23:27.866
And it's very important that they specifically go to a healing retreat for abortion

00:23:27.866 --> 00:23:30.543
not just a regular general healing retreat.

00:23:30.543 --> 00:23:32.966
It has to be for abortion.

00:23:32.966 --> 00:23:37.137
What were you doing through all these years?

00:23:37.137 --> 00:23:40.313
Were you working or studying or something else?

00:23:40.313 --> 00:23:41.922
After my healing?

00:23:41.922 --> 00:23:44.792
Yes, what was life through those years?

00:23:44.792 --> 00:23:50.286
When I was healing I felt terrible because,

00:23:50.286 --> 00:23:56.643
I was thankful to God that He forgave me but I still felt like a failure.

00:23:56.643 --> 00:24:00.722
Like I hit my lowest point, I'm never going to get a good job,

00:24:00.722 --> 00:24:03.563
no one's ever going to marry me because I had three abortions.

00:24:03.563 --> 00:24:07.240
And in the moment a man finds out, he will reject me immediately.

00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:09.971
I didn't see much for my life.

00:24:09.971 --> 00:24:12.169
I accepted God's mercy.

00:24:12.169 --> 00:24:17.079
I was happy but I I'm very surprised at what God has done in my life.

00:24:17.079 --> 00:24:21.315
I have a beautiful husband. He's like a st. Joseph.

00:24:21.315 --> 00:24:26.203
He supports me on this mission and God gave me two little girls.

00:24:26.203 --> 00:24:29.401
I didn't know if I can have a child after three abortions because

00:24:29.401 --> 00:24:32.801
when you have one abortion you run the risk of being infertile.

00:24:32.801 --> 00:24:36.597
But God's given me two little girls and I'm still trying to have more children.

00:24:36.597 --> 00:24:40.967
He's given me a beautiful family and now I'm doing His work

00:24:40.967 --> 00:24:45.569
so it it's really funny because I had abortions because I wanted to travel the world,

00:24:45.569 --> 00:24:49.256
I wanted to be successful and it was all about me.

00:24:49.256 --> 00:24:55.107
And God gave me those desires but for His glory so now I am traveling the world

00:24:55.107 --> 00:24:56.723
but it's not about me anymore.

00:24:56.723 --> 00:24:59.177
I just tell my sins, my misery.

00:24:59.177 --> 00:25:01.803
Now it's about Him and His glory.

00:25:01.803 --> 00:25:06.403
So He does fulfill the desires of your heart in a more amazing way.

00:25:06.403 --> 00:25:11.115
And what can you tell about the prayer, your prayer life,

00:25:11.115 --> 00:25:15.532
spiritual battle or everything that you gone through?

00:25:15.532 --> 00:25:19.749
So when I started to come to God and I went to my first confession,

00:25:19.749 --> 00:25:21.946
the spiritual battle was terrible.

00:25:21.946 --> 00:25:26.147
I would have demonic influence at night, attack me physically

00:25:26.147 --> 00:25:29.749
and I still go through spiritual warfare.

00:25:29.749 --> 00:25:33.320
I think a lot of us do when we serve God especially in the pro-life movement.

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:35.881
You have felt this also.

00:25:35.881 --> 00:25:44.748
Because as st. Faustina said the abbis of all hell goes against the priest.

00:25:44.748 --> 00:25:48.371
They want to knock the priest out of his vocation

00:25:48.371 --> 00:25:55.368
and then the enemy in all hell goes against humans with the sin of lust and sexuality.

00:25:55.368 --> 00:25:58.634
Abortion is a symptom, it's not the problem.

00:25:58.634 --> 00:26:02.283
The problem is disordered sexuality that we have.

00:26:02.283 --> 00:26:05.211
Abortion is just a symptom of that.

00:26:05.211 --> 00:26:07.354
So we have to go to the root, we have to fix the root.

00:26:07.354 --> 00:26:12.002
We have to tell people that they need to be virtuous and chaste.

00:26:12.002 --> 00:26:15.964
They need to live purity again. That will solve abortion.

00:26:15.964 --> 00:26:21.147
If everybody lived purity and waited for sex until marriage how it was created to be,

00:26:21.147 --> 00:26:23.011
there would not be abortion.

00:26:23.011 --> 00:26:27.602
That's the solution to abortion. Being chaste.

00:26:27.602 --> 00:26:32.068
So the attacks have been great.

00:26:32.068 --> 00:26:34.780
The spiritual warfare, the persecution is great.

00:26:34.780 --> 00:26:36.678
Also when you defend life.

00:26:36.678 --> 00:26:45.175
But we have to remember that the triumph is Lady's triumph and the victory is Jesus's.

00:26:45.175 --> 00:26:50.018
We get overwhelmed. We want to stop abortion and we think

00:26:50.018 --> 00:26:53.119
'oh the laws are getting worse or abortion is spreading like cancer'.

00:26:53.119 --> 00:26:56.052
But God doesn't call us to fix the result.

00:26:56.052 --> 00:26:58.658
He calls us to be faithful and the result is His.

00:26:58.658 --> 00:27:02.498
We know the result. He's victorious because He died on the cross.

00:27:02.498 --> 00:27:05.844
So the triumph is Jesus and our Lady's.

00:27:05.844 --> 00:27:07.869
So we just have to be faithful and serve pro-life.

00:27:07.869 --> 00:27:10.974
But my prayer life as a mother has changed, of course.

00:27:10.974 --> 00:27:16.689
I have less time to pray but little prayers throughout the day fill my whole heart.

00:27:16.689 --> 00:27:19.288
I pray now with our family.

00:27:19.288 --> 00:27:22.306
Those are little arrows in the sky.

00:27:22.306 --> 00:27:26.035
Yes but the prolifer, to the person that defend life

00:27:26.035 --> 00:27:28.987
is very important that they're in state of grace.

00:27:28.987 --> 00:27:34.234
You cannot defend life, you cannot go into this battle without literally

00:27:34.234 --> 00:27:38.484
going to confession frequently, taking the Holy Eucharist and being in a state of grace.

00:27:38.484 --> 00:27:43.164
Because what you do in the pro-life movement is that you're taking Satan's food away.

00:27:43.164 --> 00:27:46.875
Because the sacrifice of abortion is Satan's food.

00:27:46.875 --> 00:27:52.685
The baby, the soul goes to God but the killing, the murder on that abortion table -

00:27:52.685 --> 00:27:55.162
Satan's at the end of that table. He's there.

00:27:55.162 --> 00:28:00.173
He's ready to take that sacrifice so as pro-lifers we can't go into battle being weak.

00:28:00.173 --> 00:28:04.648
Or what happens sometimes that if we get too involved in activism

00:28:04.648 --> 00:28:07.367
we talk about God but we are not close to God.

00:28:07.367 --> 00:28:10.607
So we have to be very careful that we're in a state of grace

00:28:10.607 --> 00:28:16.206
and that we are fueled and we're covered with the sacraments so we can continue this battle.

00:28:16.206 --> 00:28:18.255
This is so good.

00:28:18.255 --> 00:28:23.482
I think it's so good to know how to battle this and how to go through this

00:28:23.482 --> 00:28:31.255
and not to become just active and good and like pharisees but to be like apostles.

00:28:31.255 --> 00:28:32.850
Exactly.

00:28:32.850 --> 00:28:36.674
That's so good, thank you so much. I really love this.

00:28:36.674 --> 00:28:42.479
So you were talking yesterday about the communion of the Satan,

00:28:42.479 --> 00:28:45.867
like those babies and their blood and everything that he is doing?

00:28:45.867 --> 00:28:53.974
Yes. So I feel that the root of violence in country and Mother Teresa of Calcuta

00:28:53.974 --> 00:28:59.182
has said there will never be peace in the world until there's peace in the womb.

00:28:59.182 --> 00:29:05.911
And she said in another quote don't be surprised when you hear of war in your country

00:29:05.911 --> 00:29:09.081
and people killing each other and violence,

00:29:09.081 --> 00:29:12.638
it's because it's those countries that have accepted abortion.

00:29:12.638 --> 00:29:18.309
When Our Lady of Fatima was speaking about the conversion of Russia and communism,

00:29:18.309 --> 00:29:23.001
Russia is the first country in the world that were having many abortions in hospitals

00:29:23.001 --> 00:29:25.264
even before it was legal.

00:29:25.264 --> 00:29:28.259
Russia is the first country that accepted abortion into their country.

00:29:28.259 --> 00:29:31.327
That's what our Lady of Fatima was also talking about

00:29:31.327 --> 00:29:34.088
and then after the abortion started, communism started.

00:29:34.088 --> 00:29:41.933
So Croatia have experienced war here but now war is still going on in Croatia

00:29:41.933 --> 00:29:45.086
and it's the bigger than the one that happened in the 90s

00:29:45.086 --> 00:29:48.069
because now it's children being killed by their mothers in the womb.

00:29:48.069 --> 00:29:51.552
There's nothing more awful than that. And it's still going on.

00:29:51.552 --> 00:29:58.223
A country that does not have abortion is a country that will have more peace.

00:29:58.223 --> 00:30:01.588
A country that accepts abortion like Mother Teresa of Calcuta said

00:30:01.588 --> 00:30:04.794
is the poorest country and there will always be violence.

00:30:04.794 --> 00:30:08.829
And what did you say about the friendship with the unborn children?

00:30:08.829 --> 00:30:12.533
I like that it's so sweet but it's very strong.

00:30:12.533 --> 00:30:20.185
The unborn, they don't have many friends, they have many enemies.

00:30:20.185 --> 00:30:27.989
And John 15, 15 and the Bible says that there's no greater love than to give your life for a friend

00:30:27.989 --> 00:30:32.820
and when you serve pro- life, you give your life.

00:30:32.820 --> 00:30:37.625
We don't have to die physically but we are called to die to ourselves every day

00:30:37.625 --> 00:30:42.027
and when you serve pro-life, you give your all.

00:30:42.027 --> 00:30:46.947
You're tired, you're being judged, you're being criticized, you're being bullied,

00:30:46.947 --> 00:30:52.501
you lose family members, you die, things of you die but you're giving your life

00:30:52.501 --> 00:30:55.347
for your little friends that don't have a voice.

00:30:55.347 --> 00:30:59.130
And I believe that in Jesus' eyes there's no greater love

00:30:59.130 --> 00:31:01.831
than to give your life for the pro-life movement.

00:31:01.831 --> 00:31:05.929
What is the sacrifice of being in a pro-life movement?

00:31:05.929 --> 00:31:09.197
Do you lose your family, your friends?

00:31:09.197 --> 00:31:15.943
Yes, the Bible says, Jesus says I did not come to unite, I came to cause division -

00:31:15.943 --> 00:31:20.744
mothers and fathers between daughters and sons and sisters and brothers.

00:31:20.744 --> 00:31:24.306
And that's exactly what happens when you start to defending life.

00:31:24.306 --> 00:31:28.892
You figure out who are your friends and where they stand on life.

00:31:28.892 --> 00:31:30.666
And even your family members.

00:31:30.666 --> 00:31:34.917
To this day I have controversy with my closest family members.

00:31:34.917 --> 00:31:38.859
We're divided on the issue and many of them don't speak to me.

00:31:38.859 --> 00:31:43.809
I've lost a lot of friends, I've had a lot of persecution from the abortion clinic.

00:31:43.809 --> 00:31:48.160
Also they tried to throw me in jail and I knew this when I went public

00:31:48.160 --> 00:31:52.457
but when you have peace in your heart…

00:31:52.457 --> 00:31:59.364
I always thought that peace was being on a beach in Croatia maybe and having alcohol

00:31:59.364 --> 00:32:02.491
and resting and I thought: 'oh God give me that peace'.

00:32:02.491 --> 00:32:08.455
But then a priest said to me: „No, that's not real peace. Peace actually equals strength.“

00:32:08.455 --> 00:32:17.270
He said the martyrs withstanded their martyrdom because they had peace

00:32:17.270 --> 00:32:21.745
that they were doing what God was asking them to do, that they were in God's will.

00:32:21.745 --> 00:32:28.003
And when you defend life and it's really hard and everything is going wrong around you

00:32:28.003 --> 00:32:32.730
and your family members are against you and it just feels like everything's falling apart,

00:32:32.730 --> 00:32:37.461
at least you can have peace knowing 'God this is what you've asked me to do

00:32:37.461 --> 00:32:41.455
and if I die tonight and You come for me I have peace because

00:32:41.455 --> 00:32:45.631
I know where I'm going and I'm doing what You're asking me.'

00:32:45.631 --> 00:32:51.255
That's grace. Peace is not relaxing. Peace is strength.

00:32:51.255 --> 00:32:54.690
And I just knew something.

00:32:54.690 --> 00:33:02.305
There is a difference between keeper of a peace and peacemaker

00:33:02.305 --> 00:33:06.306
because the Bible says 'blessed are a peacemaker,

00:33:06.306 --> 00:33:09.412
they should be called the sons of God'.

00:33:09.412 --> 00:33:16.086
And what I realized through my life that someone who is a keeper of a peace,

00:33:16.086 --> 00:33:21.438
he just said don't move, let it be peace, don't talk too much

00:33:21.438 --> 00:33:27.928
and if you want to be a peacemaker you have to go where the war is and make peace.

00:33:27.928 --> 00:33:29.270
Oh that's beautiful.

00:33:29.270 --> 00:33:31.308
Yes and it's really making a difference.

00:33:31.308 --> 00:33:38.323
Yes, because when you're a keeper of the peace you are silent, you don't want controversy,

00:33:38.323 --> 00:33:44.261
you are different, you're passive and you are part of the problem.

00:33:44.261 --> 00:33:47.766
So people that are indifferent about abortion

00:33:47.766 --> 00:33:51.535
are part of the problem, not the solution.

00:33:51.535 --> 00:33:57.922
What can you tell to men who needs to defend life,

00:33:57.922 --> 00:34:03.986
who have to go to the healing retreat and everything about the men population?

00:34:03.986 --> 00:34:07.276
What can you tell to them?

00:34:07.276 --> 00:34:12.765
So men, you were created for greatness, you were created to be the authority

00:34:12.765 --> 00:34:14.556
and the head of the family.

00:34:14.556 --> 00:34:21.368
You will be held accountable by God, did you protect the purity of your wife,

00:34:21.368 --> 00:34:25.316
did you protect your own purity, did you protect the way you looked at women,

00:34:25.316 --> 00:34:28.276
did you protect the purity of your children,

00:34:28.276 --> 00:34:30.485
did you protect the way your daughter was dressed

00:34:30.485 --> 00:34:34.043
or what your children saw on TV or what music they heard.

00:34:34.043 --> 00:34:36.751
Were you the great protector of their purity?

00:34:36.751 --> 00:34:42.788
St Joseph was the great protector of purity, of his own purity, of our Lady's purity and of Jesus'.

00:34:42.788 --> 00:34:44.138
Of the whole family.

00:34:44.138 --> 00:34:49.204
And it is your obligation to protect your family from the evil one

00:34:49.204 --> 00:34:53.541
and it is your obligation that your family become saints just like yourself.

00:34:53.541 --> 00:34:59.638
It's important that men regain their authority

00:34:59.638 --> 00:35:03.646
and that they become virtuous because they are the spiritual leaders of their family

00:35:03.646 --> 00:35:07.792
and when this happens a whole family is healed and a whole family is powerful.

00:35:07.792 --> 00:35:10.717
And when a family is powerful, the society starts changing.

00:35:10.717 --> 00:35:15.984
I believe that to change the world and to change society it all has to start at home.

00:35:15.984 --> 00:35:19.607
It's the family. It is the most important, the nuclear.

00:35:19.607 --> 00:35:24.925
That's why Lucia from Fatima said that the final battle between

00:35:24.925 --> 00:35:28.053
God and the kingdom of Satan will be against the family.

00:35:28.053 --> 00:35:31.073
Because it is through the family that a whole nation can heal.

00:35:31.073 --> 00:35:36.189
And for men that have had abortions it's so important,

00:35:36.189 --> 00:35:38.403
you need healing, you have to get healing.

00:35:38.403 --> 00:35:44.880
We've come to an era where there's a crisis in fatherhood.

00:35:44.880 --> 00:35:49.643
Where 80% of households around the world the head is the woman

00:35:49.643 --> 00:35:51.370
because she's a single mother.

00:35:51.370 --> 00:35:54.551
We have many men that are wounded by abortion

00:35:54.551 --> 00:35:57.632
so if you don't heal that you're never going to be a good husband,

00:35:57.632 --> 00:35:58.878
you're never going to be a good father.

00:35:58.878 --> 00:36:00.390
There's always going to be a wound there.

00:36:00.390 --> 00:36:04.739
So in order to have a strong man, a strong husband,

00:36:04.739 --> 00:36:09.158
a strong father guiding their family to holiness and to wholeness.

00:36:09.158 --> 00:36:12.931
You need to heal first.

00:36:12.931 --> 00:36:16.745
And many kids today, they have a father wound

00:36:16.745 --> 00:36:20.473
and it's a big crisis that we're facing today.

00:36:20.473 --> 00:36:25.127
Fatherless nation, fatherless generation and we need men to take responsibility

00:36:25.127 --> 00:36:28.545
for their actions and to step up and be leaders once again.

00:36:28.545 --> 00:36:33.229
And what about the women who have had an abortion

00:36:33.229 --> 00:36:38.261
or who want to abort their babies or something like that?

00:36:38.261 --> 00:36:41.051
For women who are pregnant and they're contemplating abortion,

00:36:41.051 --> 00:36:43.536
I just want to say congratulations.

00:36:43.536 --> 00:36:45.816
You are a mother already.

00:36:45.816 --> 00:36:49.945
It's not that you're going to be a mother or you're not ready to be a mother.

00:36:49.945 --> 00:36:53.620
You are a mother and I feel we don't congratulate women enough.

00:36:53.620 --> 00:36:57.493
We always come with: 'you're so young, what are you going to do, you don't have a job'.

00:36:57.493 --> 00:37:00.770
It's really instill fear. So congratulations.

00:37:00.770 --> 00:37:04.412
You're not alone, there's so much help and support,

00:37:04.412 --> 00:37:08.564
there's so many people in the pro-life movement around your area you can find,

00:37:08.564 --> 00:37:12.339
you can Google that will help you with all of your needs.

00:37:12.339 --> 00:37:16.014
It's going to be hard during your pregnancy.

00:37:16.014 --> 00:37:20.968
It's not going to be easy, that's truth but that child is going to be the light of your life.

00:37:20.968 --> 00:37:25.694
And for women who've had abortions there is hope

00:37:25.694 --> 00:37:30.217
and there's forgiveness after abortion and there's healing and there's restoration.

00:37:30.217 --> 00:37:37.014
God can restore your life and God can give you a beautiful family once again if that's His will.

00:37:37.014 --> 00:37:40.972
To look for healing, that's very important.

00:37:40.972 --> 00:37:43.826
Do you have maybe some testimonies,

00:37:43.826 --> 00:37:50.382
because I know that for many years you were at a post-abortive healing retreat.

00:37:50.382 --> 00:37:53.451
Do you have some testimonies?

00:37:53.451 --> 00:38:01.032
I have many testimonies on women who've had abortions

00:38:01.032 --> 00:38:04.781
because their parents forced them to and that happens a lot

00:38:04.781 --> 00:38:07.825
because the parents are ashamed. Because what will they say.

00:38:07.825 --> 00:38:12.072
I think when I am in those retreats it's harder for the woman

00:38:12.072 --> 00:38:14.469
to forgive their parents, more than the abortion.

00:38:14.469 --> 00:38:19.235
I've seen just miraculous healings with the whole family together,

00:38:19.235 --> 00:38:25.220
with the parents really repenting that they actually killed their own grandchild.

00:38:25.220 --> 00:38:30.693
These women walk into the retreat on a Friday afternoon,

00:38:30.693 --> 00:38:34.547
you could see it in their body, they're looking down,

00:38:34.547 --> 00:38:37.865
their body is hunched over with shame, no confidence.

00:38:37.865 --> 00:38:42.540
You could see it in their face and I see God's transfiguration

00:38:42.540 --> 00:38:44.958
in them on Sunday when they leave.

00:38:44.958 --> 00:38:48.468
Their body is up, their face is glowing,

00:38:48.468 --> 00:38:53.517
there's a smile, there's hope and you can actually physically see a miracle

00:38:53.517 --> 00:38:56.111
in two days or three days with these women.

00:38:56.111 --> 00:39:01.349
Even just the way they reflect light and healing.

00:39:01.349 --> 00:39:08.812
I have seen women who have had abortions by their own biological father,

00:39:08.812 --> 00:39:10.750
many women that have been raped.

00:39:10.750 --> 00:39:14.789
Usually rape happens within the family either the stepfather,

00:39:14.789 --> 00:39:18.996
the father or the uncle or the brother, that's very common.

00:39:18.996 --> 00:39:21.608
In postabortion healing there's a big link

00:39:21.608 --> 00:39:25.828
between rape or sexual abuse and abortion always.

00:39:25.828 --> 00:39:29.826
Most women who've had abortions there's some type of leak with

00:39:29.826 --> 00:39:33.380
sexual abuse in their childhood, that's very common.

00:39:33.380 --> 00:39:38.956
I've seen healing with that, with incest and rape and these abortion retreats

00:39:38.956 --> 00:39:43.104
not only heal the abortion because like I mentioned abortion is a symptom of something

00:39:43.104 --> 00:39:48.340
happened to you in your past or in your childhood that led you to that abortion.

00:39:48.340 --> 00:39:52.304
And what I see at these healing retreats is that not only do they heal from their abortions

00:39:52.304 --> 00:39:55.262
but they heal from wounds and trauma from their childhood as well.

00:39:55.262 --> 00:39:58.916
Patricia thank you very much.

00:39:58.916 --> 00:40:06.514
Do you have something that you would love to say to the post-abortive women and men

00:40:06.514 --> 00:40:12.039
and also to all the people why should they get involved in a pro-life movement,

00:40:12.039 --> 00:40:14.682
maybe here in Croatia with 40 Days for Life?

00:40:14.682 --> 00:40:20.717
And how do you see us here now that you spent some days here?

00:40:20.717 --> 00:40:23.275
I want to tell the men and women who've had an abortion

00:40:23.275 --> 00:40:26.505
to not be ashamed, to not fear.

00:40:26.505 --> 00:40:28.253
God's waiting for you to heal.

00:40:28.253 --> 00:40:33.276
He wants to heal that part of your life, He wants to set you free so do everything possible.

00:40:33.276 --> 00:40:35.631
The enemy will try to keep you away from a healing retreat

00:40:35.631 --> 00:40:43.697
like he did with me for 5 years but please seek a more healing on your abortion.

00:40:43.697 --> 00:40:49.366
I can guarantee you that you are going to be so grateful that you did it.

00:40:49.366 --> 00:40:53.958
And for everybody watching, abortion exists in Croatia.

00:40:53.958 --> 00:40:58.712
I think it's until the first trimester but you only need a the first trimester

00:40:58.712 --> 00:41:01.759
or a little lot to come into a country for it to get extreme.

00:41:01.759 --> 00:41:05.764
In my country, in the United States abortion is legal until the moment of birth.

00:41:05.764 --> 00:41:14.236
When a woman has an abortion at 9 months, 8 months, if the baby survives

00:41:14.236 --> 00:41:18.120
it's legal in a couple of states to kill the baby after.

00:41:18.120 --> 00:41:21.663
California legalized infanticide, a baby is born the mom doesn't want the baby anymore

00:41:21.663 --> 00:41:25.535
up to 28 days the baby can actually die and be killed.

00:41:25.535 --> 00:41:29.258
Many people don't believe my talk but this is true.

00:41:29.258 --> 00:41:32.399
We've legalized infanticide.

00:41:32.399 --> 00:41:39.289
It went from having an abortion if you were raped first trimester in our country 1973

00:41:39.289 --> 00:41:42.757
to babies now born being killed.

00:41:42.757 --> 00:41:46.733
So it's so important that you are involved in the pro-life movement,

00:41:46.733 --> 00:41:51.498
to pray for the women and men who are scared when there's a pregnancy,

00:41:51.498 --> 00:41:54.267
to pray for the conversion of abortionists and

00:41:54.267 --> 00:41:57.439
everybody that works in the abortion industry in Croatia,

00:41:57.439 --> 00:42:02.242
to actually go to these abortion clinics if you know where they are, to pray outside.

00:42:02.242 --> 00:42:05.590
Many miracles happen when you pray the rosary outside, many miracles happen.

00:42:05.590 --> 00:42:09.670
And to speak. Because God will hold you accountable.

00:42:09.670 --> 00:42:11.276
Don't be indifferent.

00:42:11.276 --> 00:42:13.257
If you know a friend that's had an abortion maybe just say

00:42:13.257 --> 00:42:16.916
'I'm praying for you, if there's anything I can do for you to help you…“

00:42:16.916 --> 00:42:20.107
Because she needs to speak to somebody.

00:42:20.107 --> 00:42:24.679
And if somebody talks about being in favor of abortion, don't be scared to speak against it.

00:42:24.679 --> 00:42:28.435
And it's so important that you have formation and education

00:42:28.435 --> 00:42:32.687
so you actually defend life and actually defend your Catholic faith.

00:42:32.687 --> 00:42:36.723
Then you can actually talk to your children about these things of the world

00:42:36.723 --> 00:42:39.829
that they're learning in school, that are not true and that can harm your children.

00:42:39.829 --> 00:42:44.199
It's just important that you're active in your formation education and that you're bold.

00:42:44.199 --> 00:42:50.536
God vomits the lukewarm, so we're living in such hard times where you can't be gray.

00:42:50.536 --> 00:42:52.351
Either you're black or you're white.

00:42:52.351 --> 00:42:56.243
You got to be - either you're for God or you're not for God

00:42:56.243 --> 00:43:00.689
and you just need to be bold and not worry about what people think.

00:43:00.689 --> 00:43:05.325
Thank you for being bold, thank you for coming to Croatia

00:43:05.325 --> 00:43:08.759
and I really appreciate having you here.

00:43:08.759 --> 00:43:09.560
Thank you Patricia.

00:43:09.560 --> 00:43:12.437
Thank you! I love this country and I love your people.

00:43:12.437 --> 00:43:15.412
I have so many gifts, I don't know how I'm going to take them home,

00:43:15.412 --> 00:43:20.005
from everybody in Croatia that's been gifting not only me but my children and my husband.

00:43:20.005 --> 00:43:22.440
So your country is beautiful and your people are beautiful.

00:43:22.440 --> 00:43:24.718
Thank you so much! 
Thank you!

